 <span data-ttu-id="33984-129">Der-Konstruktor löst eine <xref:System.ArgumentNullException> aus, wenn `alternateChoices` `null` ist oder wenn eines der Array Elemente `null`ist.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33984-129">The constructor throws an <xref:System.ArgumentNullException> when `alternateChoices` is `null` or when any of the array elements are `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="33984-130">Da die <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>-Klasse Unterstützung für die implizite Konvertierung von <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices>-, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue>-und <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey>-Objekten in <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>-Instanzen bereitstellt, kann dieser Konstruktor auch verwendet werden, um ein <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> Objekt aus einer Liste beliebiger Kombinationen dieser Objekte zu erstellen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33984-130">Because the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> class provides support for implicit conversion of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices>, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultValue>, and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SemanticResultKey> objects to <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> instances, by properly using casts, this constructor can also be used to create a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Choices> object from a list of any combination of these objects.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="33984-131">Im folgenden Beispiel werden `Choices`-und <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>-Objekte verwendet, um eine <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> für Ausdrücke wie "callanne on your Cell" und "calljames on Your Work Phone" zu erstellen.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33984-131">The following example uses `Choices` and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder> objects to create a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.Grammar> for phrases such as, "Call Anne on her cell" and "Call James on his work phone".</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="33984-132">Das Beispiel verwendet implizite Umwandlungen aus `Choices` und <xref:System.String> in <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="33984-132">The example uses implicit casts from `Choices` and <xref:System.String> to <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.GrammarBuilder>.</span></span>  
  
